measurements.description: A 240-cm x 75-cm display of diverse varieties of well-grown orchids in a wide range of sizes; dominated by specimen size dendrobiums and an arphphyllum, fronted by complex paphiopedilums, white lycastes, moss-covered hill populated by Cattleya coccinea, many color forms of Dendrobium cuthbersonii, mini-dendrobiums; centrally white with bright colors on each side of the display; also received award 20235364; AOS award 20235357 was included in display.
